## 11. Open decisions

These are the open items **as of 2026-07-04**. Anything resolved is moved to v2 shortlist or this section is updated; nothing stays open in the docs without a YAML owner + a target date.

1. **Sign-off on `v2_shortlist.md` picks.** The v2 shortlist has 4 explicit questions in its "Open for your input" block (T2 workhorse choice, cloud baseline B, AWQ-only fit acceptance, `HF_TOKEN`). Block until answered.
2. **`HF_TOKEN`** so the weekly re-scrape can include gated / private models (Meta-Llama-3.x, Mistral-Codestral, Mistral-Small-4, Yi-34B, Mixtral, etc.). The 2026-07-03 sweep was unauthenticated; gated models are missing from `models.jsonl`.
3. **Whether to keep TensorRT-LLM as `◐` for T4.** If a Blackwell GPU is added, promote to `✓`. Currently not worth the 30 min/calibration on 3090 Ti.
4. **Ling-tier fallback when 90 % promo expires.** Pre-negotiate a volume tier with OpenRouter or commit the T4 (per v2 shortlist) as primary local fallback.
5. **DeepSeek-V4-Flash-DSpark as cloud baseline B** vs `MiniMax M3` vs Claude Opus. See v2 shortlist open questions.
6. **Qwen3-Coder-Next-FP8 param count.** Needs one `HfApi.model_info(safetensors)` probe before download decision. Logged as an open item.
7. **Kimi-Linear-48B-A3B linear-attention SGLang/vLLM support.** Verify before slotting as T3.
8. **DeepSeek-V4 685 B / 1 T-MoE at home.** Not in scope on 64 GB DDR4; would need a 128 GB RAM upgrade. Skipped for this round.
9. **M1 Pro MLX-vs-llama.cpp latency profile.** Real numbers TBD; this doc's T0/T1 M1 Pro targets are aspirational.

